item.title: 【Requests】[REQ VID] - ODESZA - Coachella 2015 [1080p]
item.description:
Hello!

I've been trying to collect recordings of all of ODESZA's live sets and despite spending hours trying to find their 2015 Coachella set, I've had no luck.

They performed on Sunday April 12th in the Gobi tent. Their week 1 set was streamed on YouTube.

I managed to find a (dead) torrent for it so I know at least one person has it haha.

Thanks!
